text: Anna Maria Nieto Pedescoll (born 4 February 1991) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a goalkeeper. She has been a member of the Andorra women's national team. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers
